Thoughtless awareness, means you are absolutely aware but there is no thought.

00:54:36.487 --> 00:54:42.927
Otherwise we are always bombarded with thinking. Thoughts are coming whether you like it or not - you can't stop it.

00:54:44.267 --> 00:54:50.387
Now, thoughts come either from the future or from the past.

00:54:51.447 --> 00:54:58.747
In the present if I say, "Stop your thought," you cannot. And you cannot be in the present unless and until you stop your thoughts.

00:55:00.087 --> 00:55:05.127
So, the first state that comes to you, that you become thoughtlessly aware

00:55:05.447 --> 00:55:11.207
means you have a command over your thoughts. If you want you'll think otherwise you'll not think.

00:55:12.527 --> 00:55:17.027
And you grow spiritually only when you are in the present.

00:55:17.407 --> 00:55:22.307
If I say, "Pay attention to yourself," you can't. Say, "How to pay attention inside?"

00:55:24.627 --> 00:55:32.327
But supposing Kundalini rises, then the attention, which we can say, like a sari like this and it pushes up

00:55:33.107 --> 00:55:38.467
the attention. Attention, here, when it reaches

00:55:39.827 --> 00:55:47.727
then the Grace starts falling or you can say the light starts falling on the attention and your attention becomes enlightened.

00:55:49.987 --> 00:55:55.547
but you are in thoughtless awareness state.

00:55:57.167 --> 00:56:01.647
Afterwards, when you have established your connections properly

00:56:02.207 --> 00:56:07.587
then you are in the second state, that we call as doubtless awareness.

00:56:09.267 --> 00:56:14.727
And this doubtless awareness state in which you start manifesting all your powers -

00:56:15.087 --> 00:56:18.527
and this is what we have to achieve,

00:56:20.567 --> 00:56:27.407
which is very easy, works out in a very simple way; of course, you don't have to pay at all for that.

00:56:29.767 --> 00:56:36.007
And it works wonderfully because you get the proof of it.

00:56:39.027 --> 00:56:46.547
You get these powers working and you understand that these powers are working.

00:56:47.807 --> 00:56:55.607
You have to certify yourself - nobody is going to give you the certificate. It is you who's going to decide it.

