So mantras do not play much role, unless and until, you have that problem then you have to use the mantras

00:58:14.047 --> 00:58:19.407
but which is the chakra for which you need, you have to find out first of all.

00:58:19.687 --> 00:58:27.027
That's only possible when the Kundalini rises, then you know where there is obstructed, then you have to use a particular mantra - that helps.

